00:00:04,460 --> 00:00:09,700
Here, we'll show you how to create a split
screen view of selected tabs using Tab Tiling.

2
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:13,740
Hold down the 'Shift' key and click on the
tabs you'd like to include.

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:19,860
Once selected, right-click on one of the selected tabs and pick 'Tile Tabs' from the menu.

4
00:00:24,319 --> 00:00:30,319
To return a tab to the default view, right-click on the tab and select ‘Untile Selection.’

5
00:00:35,740 --> 00:00:36,620
Thanks for watching.

